"{\"uid\": \"indiatimes.com-trending-social-relevance-what-was-she-even-doing-at-the-olympics-the-internet-cant-get-over-lecturer-rachel-gunns-breaking-performanceheres-why-articleshow-122617553.html\", \"text\": \"I do not care, this is the greatest thing I have ever seen at the#Olympics#Breakingpic.twitter.com/BTf1cket3g  What was Rachel Gunn even doing at the OlympicsShe got cooked lolhttps://t.co/SYSkNlFgCu  Breakdancing competitions were held for the first time at the Olympics in Paris.And the main hero of this 'sport- 36-year-old Rachel Gunn from the Australian team.She did not even score a point from any of the judges. She says my dance moves were original.Do watch the video!pic.twitter.com/t3PivHGcR9  Dr Rachel \\\"Raygun\\\" Gunn, PhD in breakdancing & dance culture, Macquarie University lecturer:\\\"All my moves are original, creativity is really important to me. I go out there and I show my artistry. I do my thing, and it represents art.\\\"Yeah, art is so subjective\\u2026 \\ud83e\\udd98 \\ud83c\\udfca\\u200d\\u2640\\ufe0f \\ud83c\\udf2a\\ufe0f \\ud83d\\udc83https://t.co/ENsR2EalKH  What people do not get is that 1/2 the event is break, but the other 1/2 is a rap battle where Raygun had a significant lyrical advantage over her competitors. For ex here's her round 1 verse:Well my first name's RachelMy last name's GunnI'm coming out hereTo have some fun!https://t.co/Lre78OVhqk  I speak for everyone when I say breakdancing should not be in the Olympicspic.twitter.com/WAc2Nj09P9  GENERAL  Srishti B Dutta  You may also like  Latest Stories  Trending Now    BySaloni Jha    By    BySaloni Jha    ByNancy Jaiswal    BySaloni Jha    ByNancy Jaiswal    ByNancy Jaiswal      \"}"